premise_source_doc_sentence: Teen Wolf is a 1985 American fantasy-comedy film directed by Rod Daniel and written by Jeph Loeb and Matthew Weisman .
The film stars Michael J. Fox as a high school student who discovers that his family has an unusual pedigree when he finds himself transforming into a werewolf .
On July 9 , 2015 , Teen Wolf was renewed for a sixth season of 20 episodes , which premiered on November 15 , 2016 .
Teen Wolf is a 1985 American comedy film .
Teen Wolf is an American television series developed by Jeff Davis for MTV .
Teen Wolf premiered on June 5 , 2011 , following the 2011 MTV Movie Awards .
Teen Wolf is a supernatural drama series that follows Scott McCall  (  Tyler Posey  )  , a high school student and social outcast who is bitten by a werewolf .
